OL,3,CParties have not stood shoulder to
OL,4,Cshoulder to support police ` Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,FPolitical parties in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fhave not stood "shoulder to shoulder"
OL,9,Fto support police in the region, Jon
OL,10,FBoutcher has said.
OL,12,FThe PSNI Chief Constable told MPs that
OL,13,Fsome people from a nationalist
OL,14,Fbackground who join the force still
OL,15,Ffear that members of their community
OL,16,Fwill no longer speak to them.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
