PN,44510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774458667
OL,3,CParties have not stood shoulder to
OL,4,Cshoulder to support police ` Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,FMr Robinson said it was "important we
OL,8,Fidentify where the problems lie".
OL,10,FHe added: "My support for policing is
OL,11,Falmost unconscious, people from my
OL,12,Fcommunity, Ulster Unionists, Alliance
OL,13,Ftoo, it is unconscious.
OL,15,F"The SDLP in many ways has shown
OL,16,Fextraordinary bravery from the
OL,17,Fcreation of the PSNI to the joining of
OL,18,Fthe Policing Board and in the
OL,19,Fnationalist community, the civic
OL,20,Fnationalist community, they have
OL,21,Fstepped up to the plate."
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@`O]rD@KOUwD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
