PN,44511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774458667
OL,3,CParties have not stood shoulder to
OL,4,Cshoulder to support police ` Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,FHe added: "I don't like this notion
OL,8,Fthat it is a collective problem, the
OL,9,Fconsequence is collective, we all
OL,10,Fsuffer the consequence, there isn't a
OL,11,Fcollective problem."
OL,13,FThe DUP leader said: "Collectively I
OL,14,Fdon't think you will have any
OL,15,Fresistance with the majority of
OL,16,Fpolitical leaders or indeed the
OL,17,Fmajority of people within our
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@TO]uD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774458667
OL,3,CParties have not stood shoulder to
OL,4,Cshoulder to support police ` Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,F"I think we need to be clear about
OL,8,Fwhere the problem lies. How do we
OL,9,Faddress it?
OL,11,F"One attendance at an attestation
OL,12,Fceremony, one, once in 25 years is a
OL,13,Fdisgrace."
OL,15,FMr Boutcher said there needed to be a
OL,16,F"quiet conversations" to encourage
OL,17,Fpeople to come to a position where "we
OL,18,Fare all in the same place".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@JO]xD@AOUxD@UO]yD@dOUzD@
OL,26,AZO]
