CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774458667
OL,3,CParties have not stood shoulder to
OL,4,Cshoulder to support police ` Chief
OL,5,CConstable
OL,7,FHe added: "I don't think that happens
OL,8,Fovernight but I want it to happen in
OL,9,Fthe anniversary year of the PSNI."
OL,11,F"I am trying to do everything I can
OL,12,Fthis year....to get all the political
OL,13,Fparties, even those that have been
OL,14,Fhesitant, to come out as strongly as I
OL,15,Fwant them to, to support what we are
OL,16,Fdoing in policing.
OL,18,F"We need that to be the norm."
